    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You were caught in a storm and struck by lightning—but something saved you from death. Perhaps it was a gods-given miracle, a latent psionic gift, or the magic of a helpful elementalist, but you absorbed the lightning into your body. It’s always there now, simmering under the surface. </p><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Whenever you regain Stamina in combat, you gain 1 surge. Whenever you spend a surge to deal extra damage, you can make that extra damage into lightning damage. </p><p><strong>Drawback:</strong> Whenever you are wet, you have damage weakness 5.</p>",
